fields.name: Buttered Toast
fields.instructions:
- Put both pieces of bread in the toaster and push it down.
- When toasting is complete, apply butter liberally.

fields.name: Ham Sandwich
fields.instructions: - You should know how to make a sandwich.
fields.ingredients_text:
- 2 pieces of bread
- sliced ham
- mayo

fields.name: French Toast
fields.instructions:
- Mix everything but the bread.
- Dip your bread in it.
- Cook it for at least an hour.
- Cover in butter and syrup.
fields.ingredients_text:
- 2 eggs
- bread
- 1/2 cup milk
- 2 tablespoons sugar
- maple syrup
- butter

fields.name: Big Boy Cake
fields.instructions: Mix ingredients together and bake, slice and enjoy.
fields.ingredients_text:
* 1 lbs Flour
* 1 lbs Butter
* 1 lbs Sugar
* 1/2 lb Chocolate Chips
* 1 tsp vanilla extract
* 5 eggs

fields.name: Honey Mustard Dressing
fields.instructions: Mix all of those things together and eat on a sammich. Maybe a ham sammich.
